text: Pilar Juliana "Pia" Schramm Cayetano (born March 22, 1966) is a Filipino politician, lawyer, and television host serving as a Senator since 2019, a position she previously held from 2004 to 2016. She was also the Representative of Taguig's 2nd district from 2016 to 2019 and became one of the Deputy Speakers. Category:1966 births Category:Living people
title: Pia Cayetano
